    13	/**
    14	 * @dev WISE lending is an automated lending platform on which users can collateralize
    15	 * their assets and borrow tokens against them.
    16	 *
    17	 * Users need to pay borrow rates for debt tokens, which are reflected in a borrow APY for
    18	 * each asset type (pool). This borrow rate is variable over time and determined through the
    19	 * utilization of the pool. The bounding curve is a family of different bonding curves adjusted
    20	 * automatically by LASA (Lending Automated Scaling Algorithm). For more information, see:
    21	 * [https://wisesoft.gitbook.io/wise/wise-lending-protocol/lasa-ai]
    22	 *
    23	 * In addition to normal deposit, withdraw, borrow, and payback functions, there are other
    24	 * interacting modes:
    25	 *
    26	 * - Solely deposit and withdraw allows the user to keep their funds private, enabling
    27	 *    them to withdraw even when the pools are borrowed empty.
    28	 *
    29	 * - Aave pools  allow for maximal capital efficiency by earning aave supply APY for not
    30	 *   borrowed funds.
    31	 *
    32	 * - Special curve pools nside beefy farms can be used as collateral, opening up new usage
    33	 *   possibilities for these asset types.
    34	 *
    35	 * - Users can pay back their borrow with lending shares of the same asset type, making it
    36	 *   easier to manage their positions.
    37	 *
    38	 * - Users save their collaterals and borrows inside a position NFT, making it possible
    39	 *   to trade their whole positions or use them in second-layer contracts
    40	 *   (e.g., spot trading with PTP NFT trading platforms).
    41	 */
